  "text": "Since the particle parameters are not included in the base CosmoMC program, we instead vary N eff and m eff ν,sterile and compute the particle parameters from the chains. To accomplish this, we follow the procedure described in ref. [CITATION_1] to compute the cosmology parameters on a grid of values for ∆m 2 41 and sin 2 2θ in the ranges",
